flowRoot.flowPara: USAGE: JUST INSERT THE SIM CARD INTO YOUR PHONE AND YOU SHOULD BE GOOD TO GO! TO CHOSE A SPECIFIC PHONE NUMBER, REGISTER AN EXTENSION ON EVENTPHONE.DE AND DIAL THE GENERATED TOKEN.
NETWORK:: THIS SIM CARD ENABLES YOU TO ACCESS THE GSM NETWORK PROVIDED BY THE OSMOCOM.ORG PROJECT. LOOK OUT FOR THE NETWORK 262 (MCC) 42 (MNC).
HELP: IN CASE OF UNEXPECTED PROBLEMS OR JUST OUT OF CURIOSITY, SWING BY THE GSM ROOM, NEXT TO THE POC.
YOU CAN ALSO CALL DECT SUBSCRIBERS AND VICE VERSA.
DIAL *#100# TO SEE YOUR CURRENT EXTENSION.
